attribute.dependencies:
Can be changed to SEMI only if:
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FIXED;
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM.

Can be changed only if: 
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM; 
Abis path allocation method, set by the attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc is FLEXIBLE.

Can be changed only if: 
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM;
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE.

Can be changed only if:
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute g12Tg.tMode, is TDM;
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute g12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE.

Can be changed only if:
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM;
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE;
AMR FR with reduced codec allocation control, set by attribute G12Tg.dAmrCR, is turned on.

Can be changed only if: 
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM; 
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE.

Can be changed only if: 
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM; 
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE.

Can be changed to SCM only if:
- Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is set to FIXED;
- Transcoder connection type, set by attribute G12Tg.traCo, is set to POOL;
- Subordinate CF MO and TRXC MOs signaling type, set by attributes G12Trxc.sig and G12Cf.sig, is set to SCCONC;
- Subordinate CON MO must have DCP values, set by attributes G12Con.dcpBegin and G12Con.dcpEnd, to the values which correspond to SCM transmission mode;
- Abis path must be proper for the transmission mode SCM.

Can be changed to TDM only if EC-BCCH channel combination, set by attribute ChannelGroup.ecbcch, is not required in a cell with its channel groups connected to the TG.

Can be changed to SCM only when there are no G12Dp MOs within this TG.

To change this attribute: 
- null NRI for CS domain, set by attribute Plmn.nullNriCs, must be deleted from PLMN;
- all NRIs associated with all MSCs must be disconnected.

To change this attribute: 
- null NRI for PS domain, set by attribute Plmn.nullNriPs, must be deleted from PLMN;
-  all NRIs associated with all NSEs must be disconnected.

To change this attribute: 
- all NRIs associated with NSE related to given PLMN, set by attribute SgsnIp.nri, must be disconnected;
- null NRI for PS domain, set by attribute Plmn.nullNriPs, must be deleted from PLMN;
- the functionality GSM MOCN, set by attribute IdleModeAndPaging.mocnState, must be INACTIVE;
- all NRIs associated with all NSEs must be disconnected.
The value of the attribute sgsnNriLength can be changed only when the value of the attribute usesSgsnIp is defined.

To change this attribute: 
- all NRIs associated with MSC related to given PLMN, set by attribute Msc.nri, must be disconnected;
- null NRI for CS domain, set by attribute nullNriCs, must be deleted from PLMN;
- the functionality GSM MOCN, set by attribute IdleModeAndPaging.mocnState, must be INACTIVE;
- all NRIs associated with all MSCs must be disconnected.
The value of the attribute mscNriLength can be changed only when the value of the attribute usesMsc is defined.

Can be changed only if:
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM;
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE;
AMR FR with reduced codec allocation control, set by attribute G12Tg.dAmrCR, is turned on.

Can be changed only if:
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM;
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE.

Can be changed only if:
TG transmission mode, set by the attribute G12Tg.tMode, is TDM;
Abis path allocation method, set by attribute G12Tg.abisAlloc, is FLEXIBLE.
